<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Events at Countryside Paradise</title>
  <%- include("includes/head") %>
</head>
<body>
  <header><%- include("includes/header") %></header>
  <main>
    <section style="padding: 48px 24px; text-align: center;">
      <div>
        <img src="img/logo.jpeg" alt="Countryside Paradise logo" style="width: 128px; height: 128px; border-radius: 64px;">
        <!-- Fill src with your venue logo -->
        <br><br>
        <h1>Celebrate your special events at Countryside Paradise</h1>
        <p style="font-weight: 600; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;">
          Our spaces offer the perfect setting for weddings, birthday parties, company gatherings, and other memorable celebrations. Whether you want a rustic barn atmosphere, an outdoor reception surrounded by nature, or a lively poolside event, Countryside Paradise is ready to host it all.
        </p>
        <br>
        <a href="/book" class="card" style="padding:12px; display:inline-block;">Book your event</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section style="padding: 24px 32px;">
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <img src="img/weddings.webp" alt="Wedding celebration image" style="width: 100%; height: auto; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 12px;">
          <!-- Fill src with a photo of a wedding at the venue -->
          <h4>WEDDINGS</h4>
          <p>Exchange vows in a rustic and elegant setting. The barn, yard, and poolside areas each provide unique backdrops for ceremonies and receptions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="img/birthday.jpeg" alt="Birthday party image" style="width: 100%; height: auto; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 12px;">
          <!-- Fill src with a photo of a birthday party at the venue -->
          <h4>BIRTHDAY PARTIES</h4>
          <p>Celebrate milestones of all ages. From intimate gatherings to large parties, our spaces can be tailored for fun and memorable birthdays.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="img/company.JPG" alt="Company event image" style="width: 100%; height: auto; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 12px;">
          <!-- Fill src with a photo of a corporate or company event -->
          <h4>COMPANY EVENTS</h4>
          <p>Host meetings, team-building retreats, or holiday parties in a welcoming environment that blends relaxation with professionalism.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="img/more.jpeg" alt="Other events image" style="width: 100%; height: auto; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 12px;">
          <!-- Fill src with a photo that represents other gatherings like reunions or community events -->
          <h4>AND MORE</h4>
          <p>From family reunions to community celebrations, our versatile venue can be transformed to fit the spirit of any occasion.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <br>
  </main>
  <%- include("includes/footer") %>
</body>
</html>
